      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARCY DAKOTA (3) has an excellent record over this journey having never missed the placings in 24 starts, including 20 wins and four placings. Hit the frame latest (19.21) when second at this track in a OPEN. Looks suited and should go close. SLICK ANGEL (8) goes very well over this track and trip including two wins. Recorded a 7 length win (30.55) in a Grade 5 last time at Gawler. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. AFIRE (1) got the job done again after running them ragged to make it two in a row, scoring by 1.3 lengths (17.01) at Murray Bridge Straight over 300m. Boasts a strong record from this draw with six wins and two minor placings from 11 starts. Should be in this for a long way. STIFLER (4) best form can see him take this out.",
